[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "うう……夜の砂漠は冷えるといいますが、\nだいぶ寒くなりましたね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00971",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "まあ、今がこらえ時だよ。なんせ悪事を働く輩は、\n人通りの少ない夜を好むからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00972",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それにしてもエルスは一人で別行動とか\n大丈夫なの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00973",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボスに限っては大丈夫だと思います。\nそれに、今は街中も警戒しなきゃですから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00974",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "確かに……\n実際にイザナが攫われかけたわけだものね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00975",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "加えて今頃は武道会の真っ最中だろう？\n会場以外の警備が手薄な分、街中での犯行が怖いのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00976",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ふーん、なんとなく分かる気がするわ。とはいえ、\nこうも人けがないと聞き込みが捗らないわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00977",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あっ！　ちょっとすみません！\nおおお、お尋ねしたいことがあるんですが……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00978",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "タイニーはそれでも、手を抜かないのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00979",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……そうですか。\nありがとうございました、お気を付けて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00980",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "特に知らないそうです。また空振りでしたね～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00981",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "タイニー、気持ちは分かるけど、そんなに鼻息を\n荒くしてたら犯人じゃなくても逃げ出しちまうよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00982",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "うっ……必死なの、出ちゃってます？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00983",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そりゃもう全身から。\nにじみ出まくり、醸し出しまくり",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00984",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "うぅ、ボスみたいに鉄仮面になれれば\nいいんですけど……修行不足です、無念！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00985",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ねえ、タイニーの捜査に昼より熱が入ったのって\nやっぱり賞金首の「ヌルスラの鷹」が原因？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00986",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "同郷出身者のやらかしってのは\nやっぱりこたえるもんだろうしねぇ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00987",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……はい、それもあると思います",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00988",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヌルスラって本当はどんなとこなの？\n治安が悪かったって話だったけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00989",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "そうですね……私が小さい頃なんかは\n確かに酷かったです……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00990",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "昼でも夜でも、どこか燃えてて……\n日々の食べ物にも困る有様でしたから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00991",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "アタシも仕事柄、そういう地域をそれなりに\n見てきたけれど……大体が散々なものだった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00992",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "生きるために盗みや放火も正当化され、\nそれは子どもだって例外じゃない……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00993",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい。でも、そんな島でも私を守って、\n世話してくれた近所のお兄ちゃんがいて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00994",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ギヨームという名前なんですけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00995",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "今の私があるのもお兄ちゃんのおかげなんです。\nでも、ある時離れ離れになってしまいました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00996",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "こうして監察官になったのも、色んな島を回れるから\n監察のついでにお兄ちゃんも見つかるかなって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00997",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そっか……それがタイニーの夢なんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00998",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい。もちろん、ボスみたいな立派な監察官になって\n諸島同盟の秩序を守るってのも夢ですけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00999",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "夢は１つだけじゃなきゃいけないって\n決まりはないしね。叶うといいね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01000",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい！　話したら余計にやる気が出てきました！\n頑張らないと！　より燃えてきました！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01001",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "タイニーは、やりたいことがすでに決まってて\nそれに向かって一直線って感じね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01002",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "……お前さんだって、やりたいこと、\n見つかったんだろ？　十分立派さ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01003",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……ん、そう言ってもらえると嬉しいかも。\nタイニーもお兄ちゃんに会えるといいんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01004",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "そうだね。でもあんまり深入りするのも\n野暮ってもんだよ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "はいはい、分かってる分かってる。\n",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ようし捜査再開と……\nあれ？　燃えていたタイニーの嬢ちゃんはどこだい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01005",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "見失った！？　行方不明事件の捜査官が\n行方不明になったんじゃシャレにならないっての！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01006",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]